#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.ewm.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.ewm"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:1 of
msgid "Provide exponential weighted functions."
msgstr "提供指数加权函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Specify decay in terms of center of mass, :math:`\\alpha = 1 / (1 + "
"com),\\text{ for } com \\geq 0`."
msgstr ""
"以质心（center of mass）的形式指定衰减，:math:`\\alpha = 1 / (1 + com),\\"
"text{ 其中 } com \\geq 0`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:6 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Specify decay in terms of span, :math:`\\alpha = 2 / (span + 1),\\text{ "
"for } span \\geq 1`."
msgstr ""
"以跨度（span）的形式指定衰减，:math:`\\alpha = 2 / (span + 1),\\text{ "
"其中 } span \\geq 1`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:9 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Specify decay in terms of half-life, :math:`\\alpha = 1 - exp(log(0.5) / "
"halflife),\\text{for} halflife > 0`."
msgstr ""
"以半衰期（half-life）的形式指定衰减，:math:`\\alpha = 1 - exp(log(0.5) / "
"halflife),\\text{其中} halflife > 0`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:12 of
msgid ""
"Specify smoothing factor :math:`\\alpha` directly, :math:`0 < \\alpha "
"\\leq 1`."
msgstr "直接指定平滑因子 :math:`\\alpha`，:math:`0 < \\alpha \\leq 1`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:15 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations in window required to have a value "
"(otherwise result is NA)."
msgstr "窗口中需要具有值的最小观测数 （否则结果为 NA）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:18 of
msgid ""
"Divide by decaying adjustment factor in beginning periods to account for "
"imbalance in relative weightings (viewing EWMA as a moving average)."
msgstr ""
"在开始阶段除以衰减调整因子，以考虑 相对权重的不平衡（将 EWMA 视为移动平均"
"）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:22 of
msgid ""
"Ignore missing values when calculating weights; specify True to reproduce"
" pre-0.15.0 behavior."
msgstr "计算权重时忽略缺失值；指定 True 以重现 0.15.0 之前的行为。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:25 of
msgid ""
"The axis to use. The value 0 identifies the rows, and 1 identifies the "
"columns."
msgstr "要使用的轴。值 0 表示行，1 表示 列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:29 of
msgid "A Window sub-classed for the particular operation."
msgstr "为特定操作子类化的 Window 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rolling`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:35 of
msgid "Provides rolling window calculations."
msgstr "提供滚动窗口计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`expanding`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:38 of
msgid "Provides expanding transformations."
msgstr "提供扩展变换。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:41 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:42 of
msgid ""
"Exactly one of center of mass, span, half-life, and alpha must be "
"provided."
msgstr "必须提供质心、跨度、半衰期和 alpha 中的 恰好一个。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:44 of
msgid ""
"Allowed values and relationship between the parameters are specified in "
"the parameter descriptions above; see the link at the end of this section"
" for a detailed explanation."
msgstr ""
"允许的值以及参数之间的关系已在 上述参数描述中指定；有关详细解释，请参阅本"
"节末尾的链接。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:48 of
msgid ""
"When adjust is True (default), weighted averages are calculated using "
"weights (1-alpha)**(n-1), (1-alpha)**(n-2), ..., 1-alpha, 1."
msgstr ""
"当 adjust 为 True（默认）时，使用 权重 (1-alpha)**(n-1), (1-alpha)**(n-2)"
", ..., 1-alpha, 1 计算加权平均。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:51 of
msgid "When adjust is False, weighted averages are calculated recursively as:"
msgstr "当 adjust 为 False 时，加权平均按以下方式递归计算："

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:53 of
msgid ""
"weighted_average[0] = arg[0]; weighted_average[i] = "
"(1-alpha)*weighted_average[i-1] + alpha*arg[i]."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:56 of
msgid ""
"When ignore_na is False (default), weights are based on absolute "
"positions. For example, the weights of x and y used in calculating the "
"final weighted average of [x, None, y] are (1-alpha)**2 and 1 (if adjust "
"is True), and (1-alpha)**2 and alpha (if adjust is False)."
msgstr ""
"当 ignore_na 为 False（默认）时，权重基于绝对 位置。例如，在计算 [x, None"
", y] 的 最终加权平均时，x 和 y 的权重分别为 (1-alpha)**2 和 1（如果 "
"adjust 为 True），以及 (1-alpha)**2 和 alpha（如果 adjust 为 False）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:61 of
msgid ""
"When ignore_na is True (reproducing pre-0.15.0 behavior), weights are "
"based on relative positions. For example, the weights of x and y used in "
"calculating the final weighted average of [x, None, y] are 1-alpha and 1 "
"(if adjust is True), and 1-alpha and alpha (if adjust is False)."
msgstr ""
"当 ignore_na 为 True（重现 0.15.0 之前的行为）时，权重 基于相对位置。例如"
"，在计算 [x, None, y] 的 最终加权平均时，x 和 y 的权重分别为 1-alpha 和 1"
" （如果 adjust 为 True），以及 1-alpha 和 alpha（如果 adjust 为 False）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.window.ewm.ewm:66 of
msgid ""
"More details can be found at https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-"
"docs/stable/user_guide/computation.html#exponentially-weighted-windows"
msgstr ""
"更多详情请参见 https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/"
"computation.html#exponentially-weighted-windows"

